      <p class="title"><b>PREPARATION:</b></p>
      <li><b>1.</b> Melt the olive oil and butter in a pan.</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Chop the peppers and cook them in oil.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Add the grated tomato, black pepper, red pepper and salt and mix.</li>
      <li><b>4.</b> Add the cherry tomatoes that you have cut in the middle and turn them slightly.</li>
      <li><b>5.</b> Beat 3 eggs in a separate bowl.</li>
      <li><b>6.</b> Add the eggs to the pan, cook and serve.</li>
    
